# Client imports

This project maps `@/*` → `client/src/*` (see `tsconfig.app.json` and `vite.config.ts`).

Use `@/ui-kit`, `@/api/client`, `@/constants/...`, `@/components/...`, `@/sections/...` for cross-directory imports. Keep `./` only for siblings in the same folder.
